description:
A warm fire. A hot meal. A shadowy leader.

Written by Matthew Riddle and Alexander Williams. Featuring the voices of Carter Rockwood, Clancy Brown, Stig Michael Eldred, Nicholas Tecosky, Clayton Froning, Raphael Corkhill, Gina Rickicki, Vinny Balbo, Lauren Vogelbaum, and Geoffrey Kennedy.
